comments: Robinson (GSW) establishes his legal screening position in Holiday's (NOP) path and absorbs the contact.
Holiday (NOP) places a marginal hand to Russell's (GSW) front on the perimeter before removing the contact.
Lee (GSW) is firming up in a picking position in Hart's (NOP) path when contact occurs and he gives Hart room to avoid the contact.
Ingram (NOP) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Russell (GSW) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Williams (NOP) sets the screen in Burks's (GSW) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ingram (NOP) and Green (GSW) make incidental foot contact after Ingram releases his pass at the end of the drive.
Williams (NOP) makes marginal contact with Burks (GSW) that does not affect his ability to gather the rebound.
Redick (NOP) holds Lee (GSW) off-ball and affects his FOM.
Favors (NOP) sets the pick in Robinson III's (GSW) path and absorbs the contact when contact occurs.
Green (GSW) makes contact with the ball first, but does not dislodge it before making contact with Ingram's (NOP) arm during his shooting motion.
Holiday (NOP) and Russell (GSW) briefly engage and disengage.  Russell's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Favors (NOP) commits a take foul on Green (GSW).
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Holiday's (NOP) body during his driving shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) moves laterally into Lee's (GSW) path in transition and affects his SQBR.
Green (GSW) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Ingram (NOP).
